ure shall be posted unless the disclosure of those general means would compromise legitimate agency objectives or law enforcement purposes Each department shall implement this privacy policy by Designating which position within the department or agency is responsible for the implementation of and adherence to this privacy policy Prominently posting the policy physically in its offices and on its internet website if any Distributing the policy to each of its employees and contractors who have access to personal data Complying with the Information Practices Act Civil Code Section 1798 et seq the Public Records Act Government Code Section 6250 et seq Government Code Section 11015 5 and all other laws pertaining to information privacy Using appropriate means to successfully implement and adhere to this privacy policy PageTop Back to Top of Page aboutFTB privacy index html FTB Privacy emailapps webmaster asp Contact Webmaster Last Modified Date 11 20 2003 2003 State of California aboutFTB gsp conditions html Conditions of Use aboutFTB gsp privacy html State Privacy Policy
